SubjectFabricated Industrial Steel Components Anti-dumping and Countervailing Duty Remission Order
PrecisFABRICATED INDUSTRIAL STEEL COMPONENTS ANTI-DUMPING AND COUNTERVAILING DUTY REMISSION ORDER in order to relieve LNG Canada Development Inc. and Woodfibre LNG Limited from anti-dumping and countervailing duties on fabricated industrial steel components contained in modules used in their respective liquefied natural gas projects.
